				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have QS 1 and Summoning Haste 4 (from Firebone Notebook).  My listed casting time for Monster Summoning 2 is 7.2 seconds.  Subtract from that the benefit from Naki's ring.  With an Enshrouded Veil, I get back 5% of my mana for every pet I reclaim.  It takes me a little over 2 minutes to go from 0 to full mana,.  To say the least my DPS has skyrocketed ever since I got Suspend Minion 2.  I now chaincast nukes pretty much every fight without having to worry about running low on mana.  I pet canni during the downtime while the puller and pacifier are doing their thing.  To this day I still group with folks unaware of our mana regen capability with pet canni.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
