				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Since we aren't able to outdamage necros by any significant margin on very long fights, I can't say it's overpowered. It's just something to make up for the weakness of the mage class compared to the other casters. Without it, necros would even be better dungeon soloers than mages. All I want changed is having the casting time on suspended minion removed, since it's such an annoyance. 1 second would be good, then you'd be able to suspend the pet while moving. Apart from pet canni, the only thing we've got of any real significance ahead of necros is our better line of nukes.
<br />

<br />
With pet canni available to mages, I'd say that all caster/hybrid classes are quite well balanced. Without it, there'd be one big underpowered class.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=597626">Enharjaren Fenrirsbane</a> Arch convoker
<br />
The Celestial Rapture
<br />
