well.. lets assume that you will always get at least 30% mana preservation everytime you nuke, i am giving you the benefit of the doubt here, including items as well as spell casting mastery3.
<br />

<br />
this means, at the least you will be using 350 mana per nuke for firebolt of tallon (that is a 150 mana per shot save, everytime, again benefit of the doubt)
<br />

<br />
just 3 nukes is 1050 mana,  4 is 1400. adding in another one of your spells is even more.  and that is your best mana pres everytime you nuke.  i would like to know if it takes your group 2 minues to pull everymob so you have time to med that much mana back to use on everymob that is pulled.
<br />

<br />
add in a malo if you will of some sort and that is another 300 mana each mob, so how is it that you can regen so much mana and nuke 3-4 times per fight with firebolt of tallon.  that is a very very mana intensive spell.
